<DocsLayout
  title="Lint Rules Reference — PostgreSQL Schema Validation"
  description="Complete reference for all 75 PgDesigner lint rules: 32 errors, 21 warnings, 13 info checks. Every rule code, description, and autofix status. FK mismatches, missing indexes, naming conventions, antipatterns.">

  <p>
    PgDesigner validates your schema against 75 built-in lint rules grouped into three severity levels.
    <strong>Errors</strong> block DDL generation. <strong>Warnings</strong> indicate valid but likely
    problematic constructs. <strong>Info</strong> rules are suggestions for best practices. Rules marked
    as fixable can be resolved automatically using the autofix action.
  </p>

